ime story, voiced by the series cast.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/728240/extras/59c7199ba8eb98c902bf3aa7d5638cdc.poster.avif?t=1669902198\" width=650 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/728240/extras/59c7199ba8eb98c902bf3aa7d5638cdc.webm?t=1669902198\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/728240/extras/59c7199ba8eb98c902bf3aa7d5638cdc.mp4?t=1669902198\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
